OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA weakening
OL,6,Fband of rain moves eastwards this
OL,7,Fevening. Otherwise, showers continuing
OL,8,Facross northern areas, especially
OL,9,Fwestern Scotland and Northern Ireland,
OL,10,Fbut becoming largely dry elsewhere.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FAny lingering rain across
OL,13,Fthe far southeast will clear during
OL,14,Fthe morning, leaving many southern
OL,15,Fareas largely dry with sunny spells.
OL,16,FScattered showers elsewhere, although
OL,17,Ftending to ease later.
